
// Create a conditional statement using [if] that checks whether the value of the [.arguments] node's [stream] child is true. If so, insert all nodes referenced by the [@.invoke] expression before the first child node of [fork], and then add a [fork] node that evaluates the [@.invoke] expression.
if
   get-value:x:@.arguments/*/stream
   .lambda
      insert-before:x:./*/fork/0
         get-nodes:x:@.invoke
      fork
         eval:x:@.invoke
